reviewText: This book is more for people with experience in origami or even in math, is not for beginners. I like it once you read it you will be able to do amazing folding.

When I ordered this DVD with the picture of the twisted conical helix on the cover, I thought there would be instructions for the model.  Apparently in order to get instructions to make the more elaborate models shown, I should have ordered the book "Folding circle Tetrahedra" .  I will update again when I receive this book and see if there are instructions in the book for the models.

Shirley
